data.description: Nestled in the heart of Fairfield, this charming two-story home is a true treasure. Recently remodeled kitchen w/ granite countertops & updated appliances. The backyard has a spacious covered patio featuring a pool, creating an inviting oasis for outdoor relaxation. Enjoy the convenience of being w/in walking distance to Ault Elem. Stunning wood-tiled flooring that elegantly adorns the interior. Master down & 3 bdrms upstairs & generously sized gameroom. Recent upgrades include double-paned windows installed in 2022, a covered patio added in 2022, updated siding, new gutters, a roof replacement in 2017, & 2 HVAC units that are less than four years old. 3-car detached garage, a spacious lot, & a large pool. The formal living area could easily be transformed into a home office or study to suit your needs. With proximity to dining & shopping & access to all the wonderful amenities of Fairfield, this is a remarkable opportunity to make your dream home a reality in this coveted community.
